\s MWANA W’IMANA REMA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mwana w’Imana rema, Mwana w’Uhoraho humura\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Imana yawe muri kumwe, n’umuvyeyi atibagira./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uboneka nk’uwutariho, ariko ncuti raba uriho, uboneka nk’umukene ariko raba uri umutunzi, wiyumvirwa nk’uwapfuye, ariko ehe uri muzima\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Mwana w’isezerano, ntutinye isezerano ntiriri kure\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Ehe ngiryo riri imbere yawe Imana ni yo kwizigirwa./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uboneka nk’uwutariho, ariko ncuti raba uriho, uboneka nk’umukene ariko raba uri umutunzi, wiyumvirwa nk’uwapfuye, ariko ehe uri muzima\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Wavutse kubw’isezerano, wavyawe n’ijambo rizima\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Uhabwa Mpwemu w’isezerano none n’iki cokunyiganyiza./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uboneka nk’uwutariho, ariko ncuti raba uriho, uboneka nk’umukene ariko raba uri umutunzi, wiyumvirwa nk’uwapfuye, ariko ehe uri muzima\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Shima Imana himbaza Imana, yagutoranirije ivyiza\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Igushira mu rugo rw’intama, aho ugaburirwa utsindaje./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uboneka nk’uwutariho, ariko ncuti raba uriho, uboneka nk’umukene ariko raba uri umutunzi, wiyumvirwa nk’uwapfuye, ariko ehe uri muzima\bdit*\bd .\bd*
